lead_paragraph: Chicago's Jake Arrieta was almost unhittable and the middle of the Cubs lineup delivered at the plate in a 5-1 Game Two win over the Cleveland Indians on Wednesday which leveled the best-of-seven World Series.

headline.print_headline: Cubs Deliver in Cleveland to Level World Series
